WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:01.750
This isn't Aldershot, is it?

00:01.800 --> 00:04.450
I can't tell you how happy that makes me.

00:05.400 --> 00:07.750
Captain Page came to say goodbye.

00:07.800 --> 00:09.950
What am I going to do without you?

00:10.300 --> 00:13.250
I think you should put some
effort into being Mrs Laithwaite.

00:13.300 --> 00:15.550
