00:18.900 --> 00:20.800
I'm so glad I'm married to you.

00:22.300 --> 00:23.750
What a funny thing to say.

00:23.800 --> 00:26.750
Such close relationships
we make in army life,

00:26.800 --> 00:28.750
but we pack up and we move on.

00:28.800 --> 00:32.750
Abdul Kadir Hakim -- he'll do
anything to get rid of the British.

00:32.800 --> 00:33.800
Come back, sir!

00:36.800 --> 00:39.750
